entries.femaleVariant: Ugh… Just once, I'd like to see things go smoothly, as planned.
Is something happening?
Hmm... People are checking... Have you noticed anything out of the ordinary?
Actually... The laundry room area, I think someone was there. But earlier…
Doin' all right, all's in order?
V? What're you doing here?
Take care, V. And you keep skatin' along that edge. So fun!
Love your style, really interesting.
Headset’s nova, Lizzy…
Like it? Here, it's yours, then.
For real?
Could legitimately ask you the same…
Hah, yeah... I might be a little out of place, but I get around…
Come on. Show me where.
May I see your invitation, ma’am?
Um... sure... is everything in order?
No need to worry – routine verification. Please enjoy your evening.
Report the position of all VIPs to me. I need to know if anyone not on the guest list makes contact with them.
Almost all are located already.
Roger that. Remember – our guests' comfort is top priority. The party goes on – no disruptions.
Son of a bitch said I'd find Reed downstairs…
Time to evac, V. Best not tempt the Fates.
Head to the elevator, ride down to one. Need to know what's up with Sol.
Thinkin' about what that prick said…
NUSA’s in trouble.
Songbird is Hansen's bargaining chip.
Guy knows, got some dirt on Myers.
Songbird’s a walkin', talkin' WMD. And Hansen’s got her on a tight leash.
And he can prime her for use whenever he wants…
Yeah, heard 'im – wasn't crazy about his tone.
I need to go see what that Ziggy asshole wants.
So, the twins – ya got enough?
Sure you got everything from the Frenchies? Nothin' else needed?
Already? Was just startin' to feel the groove.
But I'm havin' such a great time.
Definitely got enough to work with. 'Sides, can't really squeeze 'em for more. Too risky.
Mhm, right. Ass in gear, now.
Sure, got loads of 'em. You’ll look like you’re on Team LizWiz. It's liable to take you places…
You and your choom best be headed the fuck out now.
Straight on from here. Gonna walk you two out.
Come on, V. No reason to hang.
All right, I'm goin'.
Move it, let's go!
Can't order me around.
Fuck you.
I'm goin', I'm goin', sheesh…
'S right you are. And no funny biz while you're at it.
Oh yeah? Make me.
No, V, let's just go.
Think you can stand there and bark orders at me? Fuck the fuck off.
Umm… I meant, uh… Please make your way to the exit…
Leavin' already?
How was the party? You have a good time?
Ignore 'em, we'll be out in moments.
No stoppin'. Le'ss go, fuck off.
Follow me.
How'd things go, V?
Got everything, all set.
That's our cue to leave!
Split up, then regroup. I'll contact you later.
Now run!
Got the sky above. Still got a tail to shake…
I'm out of the woods, too. See you soon, and watch yourself.
This feels so very, very wrong.
Can't imagine it happening, but If the public learns the NUS president willingly broke international laws governing cyberspace use…
Or you can stick aroun'…
Get down on all fours, twerk it and work it…?
It's your lucky day, you two-faced shits. Fuck outta here.
You got thorough scans of the 'runners? Both of 'em, yourself?
I want you to have it.
Hey, how ya holdin' up? Last we saw each other was… y'know…
I'mmm… doin' great. Really inspired lately. Never felt better.
Yeah… Never felt better.
Hope it stays that way. Enjoy your evening, Lizzy.
Wow. Thanks, Lizzy.
We got company! Look to the main gate!
We hold our position and wait for a window!
Look left!
They're regrouping! They'll come from the right!
Snipers! Watch out!
They're thinnin' out, V! Pile on the pressure!
Now's our chance, before they send more!
Turrets you hacked! They're really doin' it for us!
Bad news – mechs incoming!
Solid work on those mechs! They're shreddin' Hansen’s men!
Head down, V! Got it? Stay low!
Reed…
Reed!
Not the time, V.
I said we got everything.
Well, well… And then you, uh, excused yourself, stepped away, disappeared?
Hansen came by, threatened me.
How 'bout you spill where you been, what happened? Had us worried.
We were worried…
They cornered me, got me before we could meet up. Forget the rest.
Hansen showed up, we chatted. Threats were made, actually. Said if Myers doesn’t let up, world'll learn about Songbird, about piercin' the Blackwall.
entries.maleVariant: Hansen showed up, we chatted. Threats were made, actually. Said if Myers doesn’t let up, world'll learn about Songbird piercin' the Blackwall.

entries.femaleVariant: He clearly knows what So Mi means to the president.
Oh, and V – bang up work.
Hold the fuck up… You the ones who busted your way in…
Through them tunnels like eels or somethin'…
What the hell you talkin' about?
What if we did?
Uh... Got us confused with someone else, man.
entries.maleVariant: Hey, uh... Got us confused with someone else, man.

entries.femaleVariant: Yeah... Yeah, it's you.
Took out some o' my chooms. We fuckin' served together…
Maybe Hansen let you walk, but we won't.
And since he's not here, who knows what's gonna happen…
Whatcha gonna do about it?
Took out some o' my chooms. We fuckin' served together…
For what it's worth, I'm sorry. Know how you feel…
Do you?
Get the fuck outta my face.
Your friends – easy prey.
Know what it's like to lose a friend.
Try me, motherfucker.
With pleasure.
Got nothin' to say, bitch?
You're going to eat something, Lizzy, no buts. You can’t run on empty forever.
Oh, let it go, Avi. I'm a firecracker on an empty stomach, you know that. And the night is young.
I just don’t want you to pass out.
Hey, Lizzy.
Hey there, Lizzy.
Hey, Liz Wiz, famed singer, right?
Fortunately, I have darling Avi here. Avi's my new bodyguard. The best I’ve ever had, if a little too... overprotective.
Oh, it’s you… Some nerve you have just chatting me up.
After leaving me high and dry with a rotting corpse…
Just tell me where we're off to after we’re done here.
Right... We AV out to the island, where we'll hop onto a plane and fly out over the Pacific.
“The Pacific” – not a terribly precise destination, Avi…
To a private, aircraft carryin' yacht. With its own tracking system, so we’ll be flying full auto-pilot.
Ah, adventure! Yesss. Hope you’re as excited as I am!
And Dogtown, well… it always gets my blood coursing…
And you are…?
V. Just. V. Nice to meet ya.
Nice to meet you, “Just V.” Perhaps we’ll meet again someday.
We just might! Enjoy your evening.
Is there a problem, Lizzy?
Not at all, Avi. This... nobody... was leaving.
Whatev.
NUSA’s fucked.
Myers'll either have to take the fall, let herself be buried in dirt for this, or she'll defy the world and spark another war... Fuck me!
Listen, V. We need to get her out. For everyone’s sake.
Pleasure, Avi.
Leavin' already?
Lookin' like you’re about to delta outta here…
Makin' my exit soon, yeah.
But, from one party on to another! A choom of mine from Lagos is throwin' one on his yacht. Friends, fireworks, diving, a private fashion show…
Hmm... shame. Some R'n'R out on the water would do you good. But I'm sure you're, like, super busy.
Totally. Thanks.
Plus, knowing him, there's gonna be drama, so I'm totally sparing you.
Next release in the works?
Next release – planned, maybe in the works already?
Kinda... For now, though, I'm obsessed with galaxies, nebulae and sea turtles.
Uh-huh. Care to elaborate?
V, with that you know more than my producer! Patience, please, you'll just have to wait.
I'll be ready to bug outta here in five. Up to you, though.
How’d it go at the table? Anything to worry about?
Personal WMD, you mean? Yeah, Hansen knows all. Need to get 'er the fuck out, Reed, really.
I was afraid o' this... OK, V, Alex and I have work – we need to analyze the data from Songbird. Might take a day or two.
Preem. Open comms line, then?
Sure. We’ll work out a game plan, get back to you ASAP.
The op was underway, I didn't want to jeopardize it. So when confronted, I behaved.
Oh, it's up to me?
C'mon, don't act like you enjoy the jawing of these podium-pounders and career criminals.
Yeah, thought as much.
In that case, I'm gonna holo the landing pad. Unless... there's anyone else you wanna talk to...?
Well, I was hoping to have a word with Kurt 'bout that... other biz.
I can talk to him for you.
No, don't bother. Another time, I suppose.
Y 'know, you shouldn't be talking to him at all. That man means danger. Even for Lizzy Wizzy.
You know my thoughts on this.
All too well.
That mean you'll listen?
Avi, please…
